files%2F2015%2F04%2FDead-Silence-Gallery-10.jpg&h=c0bb1cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/Lone_ranger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FLone_ranger.jpg&h=4f5c9b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.青少年柴克&middot;庫柏（狄倫&middot;明尼特 飾演）和他的母親吉兒（艾美&middot;萊恩 飾演）從鄉下搬到了德拉瓦州麥迪遜的小鎮，在定居下來後，柴克認識了鄰居漢娜和過分保護她的父親「夏維斯先生」（傑克&middot;布萊克 飾演）。柴克與漢娜很快便成為了朋友，但夏維斯先生警告柴克不要越過他家的柵欄..<br />\n<br />\n2.每一個小鎮，都有著自己的鬼故事－－這種地方風格濃厚的民間傳說，往往都是小朋友們營火晚會上、夜遊時，或是到別人家過夜時，用來嚇人的最佳良伴，故事主題一般都不會離開「某個被殘殺的人，陰魂不散地想回來報仇」。而這些小孩長大以後，還會與自己的小孩共同分享這些恐怖的鬼故事，以一種代代相傳的形式，延續著這只屬於這個城鎮的小秘密..<br />\n<br />\n3.卡曼契族的精靈戰士湯頭Tonto(強尼&middot;戴普)，述說當年John Reid(艾米&middot;漢莫)如何由一個守法的檢察官變成一個象徵公義的傳奇人物。二人必須學習如何合作和跟貪污和貪婪戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n10 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK..........."},{"pid":"7b14c2a90d18bf8b226bb8d6a8ce0939016d710c","tid":328428,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4738924e830673ad3674e7caf86073eb0327f804","tid":328428,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dfa607be51909599d5cfbde113f8e0346545ee","tid":328428,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb095bac48a8289ae748e898772ff5158d02a17d","tid":328428,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 